 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Fri, 21 Nov 2014 19:49:46 +0100

linstaller (6.2.0-1) devel; urgency=medium

  * modules: added 'finish' module.
  * modules/fstab: raise the ZRAM_LIMIT barrier to 4096 megabytes.
  * modules/fstab: do not refresh the initramfs anymore.
  * config/semplice-fullscreen: do not execute the update module.
  * README.md: ensure that possible downstreams know that this project is in maintenance mode.
  * bootloader/inst: check if /sbin/init is the specified init's symlink.
  * timezone/front/glade: use preferences-system-time as header_icon
  * modules/end/front: use face-smile as header_icon and main icon
  * live-config: linstalleralan: modify the vera alan2 profile in ~/.config/vera/alan
  * debian/gbp.conf: temporairly set debian branch to debian-devel.

