linstaller (6.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * services/glade: on update_and_show_notification(),
                    properly catch eventual Exceptions.
  * linstaller.py: do not force garbage collection anymore (at least for now)
  * modules/partdisks/front: fixed display issue.
  * modules/bootloader.inst: ensure we skip eventual SD cards when installing to MBR.
  * modules/userhost/inst: cli: ensure we actually start the progressbar,
                                otherwise we will enter in a crash loop...
  * modules/bootloader: inst: ensure we take the realpath of the device.
  * modules/partdisks: front/glade: on manual_frame_creator() prefer device objects in self.changed.
  * modules/partdisks/front/glade: automatic: actually delete the disk after the user has pressed Yes.
  * modules/partdisks/front/glade: automatic_calc(): when setting up self.changed in order to switch to
                                                     the manual summary scene, properly store the device
                                                     and disk objects.
  * glade service: properly catch eventual pynotify exceptions.

