 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sat, 21 Dec 2013 18:46:02 +0100

linstaller (5.21.0-1) devel; urgency=low

  * pyparted 3.10 support.
  * services/glade: show a spinner instead of setting sensitiveness to False.
    New methods show_spinner() and hide_spinner() implemented.
  * partdisks: front/glade: use spinner when (re)building the page
  * modules/bootloader: front/glade: casper module in pre_ready() to avoid showing the page when not needed
  * glade frontend: created new status area in the buttonarea. Refactored set_header() to properly handle these style changes.
    The colors will not be used anymore in the header.
    Note: status updating when opening already touched pages is broken, as is the on_inst mode.
  * glade frontend: show notifications when doing set_header() if the window is not focused.
  * glade frontend: implemented a standard way to set the "info" header.
    The module developer now only needs to set the variables "header_title", "header_subtitle" and
    "header_icon" (all strings) to make the frontend set the header automatically.
    All .front modules have been updated to reflect this new feature.
  * glade frontend: assume defaults header to 'installing'.
  * debian/control: make linstaller-frontend-glade depend on python-notify2.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Fri, 29 Nov 2013 18:13:33 +0100

