  * bootloader: inst: I forgot the newlines :)
  * bootloader: inst: ensure we create /etc/machine-id if systemd is installed.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 03 Nov 2013 16:15:10 +0100

linstaller (5.20.0-1) devel; urgency=low

  * Hello, devel!
  * bootloader: inst: added GRUB menu hiding.
    If :bootloader:should_hide_menu:True, the GRUB menu will not be shown during boot
    if the distribution is the only operating system installed.
    This resolves project-breathe's issue #6.
  * Fixed that ugly lastres warning.
  * modulehelper: switched to importlib.
  * bootloader: custom init support.
    Use :bootloader:custom_init:/path/to/init/replacement to let the module set CMDLINE_LINUX accordingly.
  * debian/gbp.conf: restore devel-worthy things.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sat, 02 Nov 2013 01:06:47 +0100

