  * partdisks: front/glade: ensure mount_on_install is active when formatting
  * modules/partdisks: front/glade: ensure we disable eventual encrypted
    devices when in automatic.
    Also, as the automatic EFI partition is ~40 MB, ensure we use
    fat16 instead of fat32.
