    an extended partition.
  * Handle whole-drive LVM Physical Volumes.
  * partdisks/library: properly align new partitions.
  * config/semplice-base: ensure we execute mirrorselect.inst AFTER
    other modules which work with packages.
  * partdisks: ensure we properly round the maximum value of the
    size_adjustment when preparing the partition window for editing

