  * linstaller can now create LVM Volume Groups.
  * Some fine tuning and plumbing for the Edit VG mode
  * linstaller can now rename, extend and reduce existing VGs.
  * linstaller can now remove VGs.
  * linstaller can now create LVM physical volumes.
