 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Wed, 01 Aug 2012 13:26:15 +0200

linstaller (2.70.0-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * Start always the glade service if the frontend is glade. The module can now override the Back/Forward buttons: if they do not return None, the module is not changed.
  * partdisks: front/glade: added edit, remove and delete windows. Fixes here and there. Added TODO.
  * partdisks: front/glade: check if a mountpoint is already used.
  * partdisks: front/glade: Skip too small partitions; Reset header on refreshes; ensure the button are made unsensitive when populating.
  * partdisks: front/glade: implemented apply.
  * glade frontend: increased use of idle_add, thus reducing GUI crashes ;), added progressbar (and support for .inst modules)
  * modules/userhost: inst: added glade frontend.
  * modules/partdisks: library: added swap sample mountpoint
  * front/glade: moved the apply() function to a Progress-derivative class.
  * modules/welcome: front/glade: center the info box
  * linstaller.py: fixed revert.
  * modules/network: now is frontend-indep.
  * modules/fstab: made frontend-indep.
  * modules/clean: made frontend-indep.
  * modules/bootloader: ported to the glade frontend.
  * modules/mirrorselect: front/glade: properly set settings.
  * modules/mirroselect: do not update APT database if we aren't on the last set.
  * modules/mirrorselect: inst/glade: added.
  * some fixes
  * modules/language and modules/timezone: switched to keeptalking.
  * modules/language and modules/timezone: Added glade frontends for front, basing on keeptalking (I <3 KEEPTALKING)
  * core/module.py: ensure we properly save and reload module's settings when reopening an already opened module.
  * modules/language and modules/timezone: added inst.
  * linstaller.py: handle arguments with spaces when doing fullrestart.
  * frontends/glade and services/glade: ensure the next button is insensitive on inst.
  * setup.py: changed to install glade frontend/services; now at 2.70.0!
  * added glade frontend.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Tue, 31 Jul 2012 23:15:19 +0200

