  * debian/: Every package is supported by all architectures.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 24 Jun 2012 17:38:29 +0200

linstaller (2.14.0-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * Services support (Modules which runs on threads)
  * New glade frontend (gtk3, every module has its own glade file)
  * Glade service (preloads the glade files and shows the gtk3 window)
  * Other minor things
  * modules/userhost: added and completed glade frontend.
  * linstaller.py: if module is preseeded, add _preexecuted to its seeds
  * linstaller.py: "casper" return status: it returns the old module's return status
  * frontends/glade: implemented steps, some more signals
  * services/glade: added header.
  * services/glade: change_entry_status() which changes an entry's secondary icon with icons that matches the header.
  * modules/mirrorselect: added glade frontend.
  * modules/welcome: glade: added the "how to use this application" section
  * frontends/glade and services/glade (and core/): support on_caspered signal.
  * modules/: made the glade frontends less crashy and faster
  * Moved README to README.md
  * Updated README.md
  * modules/partdisks/front: added some bits of the glade frontend.
  * modules/raspberrypi: added
  * config/: added semplice-raspberrypi configuration. setup.py: ship raspberrypi config and module.
  
  * debian/:
    - added linstaller-config-semplice-raspberrypi and linstaller-modules-raspberrypi packages.
    - Bumped to Standards-Version: 3.9.3.1.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 24 Jun 2012 15:46:02 +0200

linstaller (2.13.3-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * do not format swap partition by default.
  * debian/:
    - make echo depend on extlinux, too.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Mon, 30 Apr 2012 18:07:58 +0200

linstaller (2.13.2-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * alan: Added an item to start echo. mouldes/fstab: correctly sort partitions before generating the fstab.
  * Some changes to gtk3 frontend.
  * fixed fstab loop.
  * partdisks: library: do not crash if we reach partition limit in automatic.
  * as above.
  * partdisks: library: fixed indentation error, try/except in swap, too.
  * modules/echo.partusb: frontend: removed useless seeds. linstaller.py: new -r|--remove argument which specifies the modules to remove from list.
  * modules/echo.partusb: frontend: added new seed "allfreespace", does not calculate the freespace by checking the freespace and removing the image's files
  * modules/echo.partusb: added support for 'type'
  * config/semplice-persistent: removed erroneous preseed to syslinux
  * modules/echo.bootloader: inst: some changes to bootloader installation, still to refine.
  * modules/mirrorselect: install: do not crash if mirrorselect crashes.
  * modules/echo.bootloader: install: fixed extlinux installation
  * release 2.13.2.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Tue, 24 Apr 2012 19:10:23 +0200

