  * setup.py: ship ubuntu and ubuntu-nolive configs.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 19 Feb 2012 16:22:31 +0100

linstaller (2.11.0-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * fstab: fixed automounting of vfat partitions.
  * config/: added ubuntu and ubuntu-nolive configurations.
  * modules/clean: search for /linstaller in target and, if any, delete it
  * modules/debian: ensure dpkg is configured before starting removing pkgs
  * modules/ubuntu: added, recompiles python modules and copies the kernel
    from the image.
  * setup.py: ship the ubuntu module.
  * debian/:
    - Added linstaller-config-ubuntu package
    - Added linstaller-modules-ubuntu package
    - linstaller-config-semplice now depends on linstaller and modules-base
  * modules/summary: print all changed partitions instead of only / and swap
  * modules/fstab: handle mountpoints not handled by partdisks
  * modules/partdisks: inst: sort partition list by mountpoint; when revert(),
    use the reverse of "used".
  * config/semplice-base and config/ubuntu: moved fstab.inst before end.front.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 19 Feb 2012 16:16:11 +0100

