  * config/semplice-base: execute network.inst too
  * modules/network: copy host's resolv.conf to the target
  * modules/mirrorselect: correctly close the chroot if the prechecks
    returns False.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 05 Feb 2012 19:47:04 +0100

linstaller (2.10.6-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * linstaller.py: populate modules_settings from the inline
    preseeds.
  * partdisks: library: mount_partition can now skip mountpoint check
    if check == False.
  * partdisks: library: fixed opts handling if remounting.
  * partdisks: inst: do not require "changed" from frontend.
  * partdisks: inst: bind-mount /dev, /sys and /proc (moved from
    unsquash).
  * frontends/gtk3: errors and steps handling.
  * userhost: gtk3 frontend: completed.
  * frontends/gtk3: exit from the loop via a thread; fixed button sequence;
    line_wrap on new text; new section object (doesn't work); fixed
    reset_position; override start action: modules should use the gtk_start
    function instead.
  * userhost: gtk3 frontend: use section (doesn't work).

