  * core/cli_frontend: new progressbar wrapper (class __ProgressBar).

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Tue, 13 Dec 2011 18:01:39 +0100

linstaller (1.52.4-1) emily; urgency=low

  * modules/partdisks: frontend: preseed root_noformat and swap_noformat
    if already formatted via edit_partitions.
    Reduces disk stress and should fix a crash when starting from an empty
    disk.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Thu, 08 Dec 2011 14:09:06 +0100

