  * modules/partdisks: always declare choices[num] while printing
    partitions; pull self.changed obj from choices[num] instead of
    hardcoding to disk; do the partition table creation *before*
    committing in the object (and before that, remove the device
    from touched).

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Mon, 28 Nov 2011 18:47:09 +0100

